net.floodlightcontroller.core

接口 Deliverable<T>

  • 类型参数:
    T - type of the result of the computation
    所有已知实现类:
    DeliverableListenableFuture

    public interface Deliverable<T>
    abstracts the 'back side' of a Future that is being listened on, i.e., an object that receives a result or an error of the computaton once it is ready. A deliverable can accept multiple computation results, indicated by the return value of deliver.
    作者:
    Andreas Wundsam
